high_descs: Turn left and Walk few steps straight and turn right and go out from the bed room and turn left walk towards to the living room and turn right and walk towards to the kitchen room sink.
Get the mug from the kitchen table.
Take the cup and put it on the sink.
Wash the cup and take back from the countertop.
Place the mug on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Take the mug from the countertop, wash it and place it on the same place again.

high_descs: Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the table.
Pick up mug from the table.
Head straight towards the counter top by turning around and turning left.
Move little bit back from the counter top
Place mug on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Shifting mug from one place to another.

high_descs: Head to the room exit on the left side of the front wall, then turn immediately left, step into the hall and head right in a kitchen corner, where you step in front of the sink right up front.
Pick up the mug from next to the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, rinse the cup out, then take the cup back out.
Place the mug in the lower left corner of the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed-out mug on the countertop.
